                <h2 class="article-title">
                    <a href="https://digg.one/c/news">Digg.one REST API now alpha and in development and already working</a>
                    <a href="https://digg.one/c/news"
                        class="article-source">(digg.one)</a>
                </h2>
                <div class="article-meta">
                    <span class="article-score">7 points</span>
                    by
                    <a
                        class="link article-author" href="/users/members/graham">graham</a>

                                        <span class="article-time">
                        507
